                <h1>Mastering the iPhone App Switcher: A Quick Guide</h1>
                <p>The app switcher on iPhone allows users to quickly navigate between recently used apps, enhancing multitasking efficiency. To access it, simply swipe up from the bottom of the screen (or double-tap the home button on older models). Users can close apps by swiping them off the screen, offering better performance.</p>
